metadata.name: Eagle in the Sky
metadata.description:
Like an eagle in the sky,
The F-15 fighter jet soars high.
A symbol of freedom, strength, and might,
It's a bird of prey, ready to fight. 

Its wingspan vast, its engines roar,
It cuts through the air, like an eagle for sure.
With precision and speed, it takes flight,
On a mission to protect, to defend what's right.

Fly High is the collection of fighter jets across the world. The Optical illusion illustration effects gives a feel that the jet is flying over a terrain.

An OPI originals.
